{"tid":309001,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[1月新番] CHAOS;CHILD 混沌之子 第13話  -SILENT SKY-","createTime":"2017-07-04T15:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T03:08:56.000Z","uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37570b3fadbe7fe13408d1a52bac6fbd8ec22534","tid":309001,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://chaoschildanime.com/img/main2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchaoschildanime.com%2Fimg%2Fmain2.jpg&h=b4c9a76b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介<br />\n《混沌之子（CHAOS；CHILD）》是 5pb. 所推出的第四部作品，亦是妄想科學系列第一部《混沌思緒 諾亞（CHAOS;HEAD NOAH） 》的續作。<br />\n<br />\n澀谷因為前作後期發生的大地震而被摧毀，前作的 6 年後， 2015 年 10 月，澀谷已經重建完畢，復興中的澀谷連續出現奇妙的怪死事件──身為實況主的男子在自家直播中離奇死亡、在東京澀谷街頭演唱的女歌手因不明原因猝死&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n碧朋學園新聞部部長 宮代拓留因緣際會之下，注意到這兩起事件跟 2009 年發生連串獵奇殺人事件「新世代的瘋狂（NewGene）」的首兩則事件的發生日期相同。就在持續調查與種種事件的牽引之下，宮代等人逐漸陷入事件的核心&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原作:志倉千代丸／MAGES.<br />\n監督・シリーズ構成:神保昌登<br />\n脚本監修:林直孝、梅原英司、松原達也、松本裕介<br />\nAnimation制作:SILVER LINK.<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n宮代拓留:松岡禎丞<br />\n尾上世莉架:上坂すみれ<br />\n来栖乃々:ブリドカットセーラ恵美<br />\n有村雛絵:三森すずこ<br />\n山添うき:水瀬いのり<br />\n香月華:仲谷明香<br />\n久野里澪:真田アサミ<br />\n<br />\n網站: <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chaoschild.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chaoschild.com%2F&d=f8sYqzT8xM3CTke186hn3QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ecf1e8ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chaoschild.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n線上<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://himado.in/391239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimado.in%2F391239&d=f8sYqzT8xM3CTke186hn3QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3bb2541e\" target=\"_blank\">http://himado.in/391239</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-41960-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-41960-1-1.html&d=f8sYqzT8xM3CTke186hn3QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=eb15eb05\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-41960-1-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"ca6ee35c69b01ab363bc384cc6f9c4ce8b384c9b","tid":309001,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"牙井好波"},{"pid":"816b0fdef24dcb2b955c69a963b901a6adceaac5","tid":309001,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"13話 呢話講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c61772ee42a093a0f8b8263ca7b5cf692146ee4","tid":309001,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T15:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2552fd6b6fc603f489b3a314c444e9aa5bf4d0a","tid":309001,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T01:34:30.000Z","msg":"A,B<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://himado.in/391239\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimado.in%2F391239&d=f8sYqzT8xM3CTke186hn3QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=3bb2541e\" target=\"_blank\">http://himado.in/391239</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://himado.in/391256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhimado.in%2F391256&d=f8sYqzT8xM3CTke186hn3QRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2e7ba05f\" target=\"_blank\">http://himado.in/391256</a>"},{"pid":"5a1f037a7df685b8fa36d76a732503581449029e","tid":309001,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>13話 呢話講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n垃圾到冇朋友"},{"pid":"d9d99f367bbfa0962f142af83cef550f433252de","tid":309001,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"つまんねえ"},{"pid":"ca660c769612d6dc3bd223b1e020a6705f5d76db","tid":309001,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T02:56:04.000Z","msg":"得第一集宮崎羽衣出山最有睇頭<br />\n<br />\n之後全部都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class